        {
            "title": "蘋果季度營收強勁 但大中華銷售遠遜分析師預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 蘋果公司第四財季中國營收大幅低於分析師預期，抵消了當季整體銷售強勁帶來的積極影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公司周四在一份聲明中表示，截至9月27日當季，大中華區營收下降3.6%，至145億美元，遠遜於分析師此前預期的164億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">總營收為1025億美元，略高於市場普遍預期的1022億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一結果再度令外界擔憂蘋果的中國市場占有率正在逐漸流失。該公司在當地面臨中國本土智慧手機品牌日益激烈的競爭，而且在華AI功能的推出也遇到阻力。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c07e29f5-6675-339e-aa94-80927cc33ccd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與往常一樣，蘋果本次未在財報中提供對當前季度的業績展望。該公司預計將在財報電話會議中給出部分前瞻性評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Apple Posts Disappointing Sales in China, Marring Upbeat Report</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81-%E4%BD%86%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%81%A0%E9%81%9C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-204751856.html",
